{"tid":1382897,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[救命用]口罩使用教學(6500系列/7500系列/N95)","createTime":"2019-07-29T14:46:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T17:16:36.000Z","uid":104255,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4d73f3d5673839e743c53f41b1a33a6e9d9e4d5f","tid":1382897,"uid":104255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:46:34.000Z","msg":"大家發夢為左防TG，買左好多SSR裝同SR裝(3M 7500/6500)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有前線巴絲反映，明明戴左神裝，點解一樣會食到TG？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">因為你唔撚識戴！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">戴錯口罩=無戴口罩！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n要check個口罩戴得正唔正確，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係有方法既</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n去片：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DzIDhYGnDIM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDzIDhYGnDIM&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiVR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=3e2b2f84\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DzIDhYGnDIM</a><br />\n<br />\n所有Mask(6500/7500/N95)都係需要做2個test:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">Positive Pressure Test 同 Negative Pressure Test</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">6500/7500系列：<br />\n1) Positive Pressure Test:</span><br />\n主要係試呼氣會唔會漏氣同個罩貼唔貼面，<span style=\"color: red;\">極趕時間時都最少做左呢個先。</span><br />\n方法：壓住出氣口呼氣（中間個位），如果口罩谷起左無漏氣就算ok。有漏氣就索返緊個罩啦。詳細可睇片<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">2）Negative Pressure Test:</span><br />\n呢個係試吸氣會唔會漏氣，趕時間就skip啦<br />\n方法：60926用手遮住個罐罐吸氣，2097就篤住個中間位試（502/mask個接口位）個口罩識縮入去邊位無漏氣就叫合格。邊位有氣入一樣，索緊佢<br />\n<br />\nN95:<br />\n中後排好多時候都無神裝，而N95都係要做測試既：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pGXiUyAoEd8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpGXiUyAoEd8&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiVR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=f4cbb5b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pGXiUyAoEd8</a><br />\n3:25開始睇<br />\n<br />\n基本上就係用手遮住哂口罩分別試吸氣同呼氣，如果戴得好就應該唔會漏氣的。<br />\n<br />\n搞唔掂的話就用返普通口罩/濕水面巾啦，<span style=\"color: red;\">點都好過戴錯既N95</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望唔好再有人因為TG入罩而被迫除罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命！！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"01d93d7f93afaa7ef143cfe123473cac2512d829","tid":1382897,"uid":52364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:46:54.000Z","msg":"阻阻大家<br />\n[港鐵不合作運動] 站長有幾點要提大家！！！<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1382840/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1382840/page/1</a><br />\n大家幫手推畀其他人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6493489b126217fca0d3f44c972372168694afc3","tid":1382897,"uid":104255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:49:31.000Z","msg":"805 大三罷"},{"pid":"d9d012681977c337cd5b2708e5684d647a00e95b","tid":1382897,"uid":104255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:57:13.000Z","msg":"805 大三罷"},{"pid":"b255ef859cc8273c649e4059c9225247282d9155","tid":1382897,"uid":263367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:01:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0f4c4948f34f3ba0cd5318d69051316a88265dc6","tid":1382897,"uid":104255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:10:32.000Z","msg":"805 大三罷"},{"pid":"5cf62022bd5645f329fee45d1908891906e3adea","tid":1382897,"uid":104255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:09:58.000Z","msg":"805 大三罷"},{"pid":"8bac4dcc5b7aa2f5e21df5e7e74e63f78e38d2fc","tid":1382897,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:43:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3fd29bf5532e326ea28b0e7b01256addc180a8cc","tid":1382897,"uid":104255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:29:36.000Z","msg":"805 大三罷"},{"pid":"363b45eaef26c62ec457f0c1e69953d746ceffb9","tid":1382897,"uid":36761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T17:16:36.000Z","msg":"R95 口罩 有效擋到彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最平$20有找<br />\n<br />\n推"}]}